{"tid":1898853,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致全港嘅泛民議員：除投票反對預算案，請設法令警隊撥款分開審議","createTime":"2020-02-26T09:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-26T09:42:07.000Z","uid":286309,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"78b12cb6004d61b8fc228dd65d97d03909bf6b5b","tid":1898853,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:21:13.000Z","msg":"背景：<br />\n<br />\n今次預算案完全係一個政治操作<br />\n港共之所以咁佛心人人一萬<br />\n因為佢地預左<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">未必</span></strong></span>過得到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">過唔過預算案港共都站喺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">道德高地</span></span></span><br />\n\b<br />\n區議會議員： <br />\n<br />\n請喺可行嘅時間內，17區聯會動議「支持」立法會<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">分開審議</span></span></strong>警隊預算<br />\n純粹為一個宣傳手法<br />\n要令媒體免費可以報導相關信息<br />\n擴大社會意識<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>善用區會平台大造輿論</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員：<br />\n你地已經處於兩難局面<br />\n因為民生嘅撥款同黑警嘅撥款，喺現有嘅局面下係捆綁緊<br />\n暫時只有投Yes / No <br />\n呢個正係港共想要嘅陰謀<br />\n<br />\n要解決呢個困局<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n<br />\n唯有用盡你地已知嘅方法<br />\n分開警隊嘅撥款去審議<br />\n<br />\n</strong></span>波叔做緊主席係難啲，不過希望你地可以搵到方法啦。"},{"pid":"73026aafeee3f905523a01be0ac67fe5070a783a","tid":1898853,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:22:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5135be8c9667c06505198a0f6d213e05730a994e","tid":1898853,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:24:08.000Z","msg":"我指緊嘅係傳統泛民<br />\n民主黨＋工黨＋社民連＋公民黨 etc"},{"pid":"9fa17ebd0b30726beaa6ba39785bc5bfce3b19d5","tid":1898853,"uid":134744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T09:25:10.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n同埋隔離個post講萬三thx都有得諗"},{"pid":"5d40dc3135a1fd7221e889179d1d96927a4a679e","tid":1898853,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"